description: These are the kaomojis that are related to food. Sorting these out into one section for food and one for drink is pretty much the only way to go here. They are eating kabobs, soup, birthday cakes.. you name it! There is even some cool looking text that says “I love chocolate!” I figured a lot of people could relate to that one!
